content:
The fifth and final step in Decision Optimization is to review and save your new optimization.

To confirm and save your optimization:

Review your optimization, and make changes as needed.
Click Save.
Name your optimization, and select whether you want to generate a new dataset to explore the results. The generated results dataset is placed in your private folder.
NOTE The generated optimization results dataset counts toward your dataset row storage in CRM Analytics.

Click Save & Run.

EXAMPLE Use a generated dataset to explore the results of the optimization for your data. For example, you can see the weighted values of opportunities in the pipeline. You can also measure the data against the constraints that you configured.

SEE ALSO
Limits and Considerations for Decision Optimization (Beta)
title: Reviewing and Saving Decision Optimization Results
